Package net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.window

Class WindowImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.window.WindowImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Window
    public class WindowImpl
extends Object
implements Window
    A test implementation of the Window interface. This class is used for testing the window builder infrastructure. Properties exposed by the interface are simply stored in member variables.
    Version:
    $Id: WindowImpl.java 205 2012-01-29 18:29:57Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger
